caption.p: The effect of GOEO on migration of cancer cells. ( a) HepG2 cells; ( b) HepG2 cells treated with 0.3 μL/mL of GOEO; ( c) HCT116 cells; ( d) HCT116 cells treated with 0.3 μL/mL of GOEO; ( e) Percentage of migration cells compared with the control group. The cell mobility of the control was set to 100%.
